data.description: Recent price improvement! The California buyer's financing fell thru! So their loss is your gain! Sellers have been transferred out of state. Such an adorable 3br/2ba home in a great location and on a corner lot! Fenced in back yard for the babies, human or furry! Nice large back deck right off dining room with a new sliding door..a great outdoor entertaining space. LOTS of updates including new light fixtures, Life-Proof flooring and the kitchen has new granite countertops AND the appliances were replaced in 2021. The living room has a new front door(& storm door). As well as a one year old roof (put in summer of 22). There is a bedroom downstairs with full bath access, and there are 2 bedrooms upstairs and laundry room/2nd bath is also upstairs.This home is in such a good central location, and a quiet neighborhood just 5 minutes to Amazon (former Knoxville center) shopping & dining and just 10 minutes to downtown, 15 min to UT Hospital, 20 to West Knox, 20 minutes to airport.  **Balcony outside of master is decorative only** Please don't walk on it.Prefer to close where title work has already been done-Scruffy City Title**
